PARKWAY GENERATION SEWAREN URBAN RENEWAL ENTITY LLC
Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service Parkway Generation Sewaren Urban Renewal Entity LLC ("Parkway Gen Sewaren") provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ("Reactive Supply Service") from a generating facility located in Woodbridge, New Jersey to the PJM Interconnection, L.L.C. ("PJM") system. This Rate Schedule sets forth Parkway Gen Sewaren's revenue requirement for the provision of Reactive Service from the facility pursuant to Schedule 2 of the PJM Open Access Transmission Tariff, which provides for PJM to pay generation owners their monthly revenue requirements for Reactive Service.
This Rate Schedule shall be effective upon the date authorized by the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission.
REVENUE REQUIREMENT Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $2,601,677. Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $216,806.41.
